 _P_o_d_z_i_m_n_i_ _p_a_v [Muž] [Kategorie]
18.12.2007 17:39:29
Tohle makro například nastavuje v měsíci soboty a neděle šedou barvu buňky.

Private Sub ButtonOK_Click()
Application.ScreenUpdating = False
Dim dat
Range("Datum" ) = Range("A9:A39")
dat = DateValue(Datum1)
Range("B5").Select
ActiveCell.Formula = dat
Range("A9").Select
ActiveCell.Formula = dat
Range("A9:A39").Se lect
Selection.DataSeries Rowcol:=xlColumns, Type:=xlChronological, Date:= _
xlDay, Step:=1, Trend:=False
Range("A9").Select
měsíc = Month(dat)
For a = 1 To 31
Range("Datum").Cel ls(a).Select
dat = Range("Datum").Cel ls(a)
měsíc1 = Month(dat)
If měsíc <> měsíc1 Then
Range("Datum").Cel ls(a).Select
Range("Datum").Cel ls(a).EntireRow.Hidden = True
Else
Range("Datum").Cel ls(a).EntireRow.Hidden = False
End If
If WeekDay(dat, 2) = 6 Then
Selection.Interior.ColorIndex = 15
Else
Selection.Interior.ColorIndex = 2
End If
If WeekDay(dat, 2) = 7 Then
Selection.Interior.ColorIndex = 15
End If
Next a
